12:21.240 --> 12:30.600
and what we do first is to
use this circuit description to create a new circuit that implements a controlled U operation like
is pictured on the screen.

114
12:30.600 --> 12:37.230
This is pretty simple to do. What we can do is to add a control Qubit, which is pictured on
